+ Request (application/json)

    + Attributes
        + task_id: 1 (number, required) - Id of the task

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Attributes
        + state: success (string)

### getTasks.php [POST /getTasks.php]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Attributes
        + amount: `25` (number, required) - The amount of tasks returned per request
        + pageno: `0` (number, required) - The current page
        + selected_customfields: `42,142` (string) - Comma-separated list of the Id's of the custom fields you wish to select
        + user_id: `1` (number) - Rreturn only tasks for this user

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Attributes (array[Task])

